1. Basic Design concept 

please see ./discovery_design_concept.png  for details

2. To run the demo

[1] Install the latest Node.js 
[2] Install latest socket.io codes (tested on 0.7.7)
    npm install socket.io
[3] start Server side script 

    node Server/DiscoveryServer.js

[4] start client side script

     google-chrome ./discovery.html
	
[5] select service type. e.g. handset service

[6] Give a few second, the found devices shall display.


Happy Discovery!

Contact ziran.sun@samsung.com if you need more information. 	     
